## Step 8

Now we need to add a `Stack` for our octave:

``` dart
 return SafeArea(
               child: Stack(children: <Widget>[
                 Row(mainAxisSize: MainAxisSize.min, children: <Widget>[
                   _buildKey(24 + i, false),
                   _buildKey(26 + i, false),
                   _buildKey(28 + i, false),
